---
title: Seared Chicken & Herby Hollandaise with Roast Potato Chunks & Apple Slaw
description: Hello, did someone call for one amazing chicken dinner special? We are ready to serve you up one with a herby
hollandaise for a fragrant sauce and the roast potatoes boost this experience up to a five-star level. We recommend
you dig in straight away!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
